snippet.title: NARAKA: BLADEPOINT OFFICIAL GAMEPLAY TRAILER | Forerunner Beta Starts on 4.23
snippet.description:
Check out the latest gameplay trailer and join the FORERUNNER Beta of NARAKA: BLADEPOINT, the fast-paced Action Royale featuring adrenaline-pumping melee combat. Wishlist & Join Playtest Now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1203220/NARAKA_BLADEPOINT/
FORERUNNER Beta Date: Apr 23rd - 25th PDT
Region: Global
Platform: Steam

Twitter: https://bit.ly/36FVKOB
Discord: https://bit.ly/3iUZboz​
